Romilly Lunge https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romilly_Lunge 0 Romilly Lunge (1904–1994) was a British film actor. He made a total of 15 films and appeared in many stage plays between 1933 and 1940. He died in August 1994 in Leicestershire, England. Romilly_Lunge ( 1904 – 1994 ) was a_British_film_actor . He made a_total of 15_films and appeared in many_stage plays between 1933_and_1940 .
